Seems no option to reopen the closed issue,

Could you please clarify this 

https://github.com/xamarin/Xamarin.Forms/issues/4317

Can you please modify the sample shared to achieve my requirement,

I have tested the same, you can find the demo sample in arrange override could not raised only measure override called, 

Please test the sample  https://github.com/xamarin/Xamarin.Forms/issues/4317 .    protected override Size ArrangeOverride(Size finalSize) not calling . only measure override called .

` public sealed class CustomControl1 : Control
    {
        public CustomControl1()
        {
            this.DefaultStyleKey = typeof(CustomControl1);
        }

        protected override void OnApplyTemplate()
        {
            base.OnApplyTemplate();
            this.SizeChanged += CustomControl1_SizeChanged;
        }

        private void CustomControl1_SizeChanged(object sender, SizeChangedEventArgs e)
        {
        }

        protected override Size MeasureOverride(Size availableSize)
        {
            return base.MeasureOverride(availableSize);
        }

        protected override Size ArrangeOverride(Size finalSize)
        {
            return base.ArrangeOverride(finalSize);
        }
    }`

I did not know ,Why size cahnged event not fired in below settings , especially on minizing in below mentioned scenario? 
Custom Control HorizontalOptions and VerticalOptions to be FillAndExpand

Custom Control SizeChanged event not fired when minimize the page , but custom control MeasureOverride size get changed when application size get changed.
